{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"我的命令只是快如转瞬的一句话。"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"我确已将你们的宗派毁灭了。有接受劝告的人吗？"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"凡他们所做的事，都记载在天经中。"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"一切小事和大事，都是被记录的。"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"敬畏的人们，必定在乐园里，在各种河岸边，"},{"SurahNumber":54,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"在全能的主那里，得居一个如意的地位。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"至仁主，"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"曾教授《古兰经》，"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他创造了人，"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"并教人修辞。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"日月是依定数而运行的。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"草木是顺从他的意旨的。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他曾将天升起。他曾规定公平，"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"以免你们用秤不公。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"你们应当秉公地谨守衡度，你们不要使所称之物分量不足。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"他为众生而将大地放下。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"大地上有水果，和有花篦的海枣，"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"与有秆的五谷和香草。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"你们究竟否认你们的主的哪一件恩典呢？"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"他曾用陶器般的干土创造人，"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"他用火焰创造精灵。"},{"SurahNumber":55,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"你们究竟否认你们的主的哪一件恩典呢？"}]}